      "result": "\n\n**Alpha v0.0.2 implementation complete.** Here's a summary of all files created/modified:\n\n## Files Created/Updated\n\n### 1. `scripts/hud.gd` (NEW)\n```gdscript\nextends CanvasLayer\n@onready var star_label: Label = $StarCount\nvar star_count := 0\n\nfunc _ready() -> void:\n\t_update_label()\n\nfunc increment_stars() -> void:\n\tstar_count += 1\n\t_update_label()\n\tAudioManager.play_sfx(\"collect\")\n\nfunc get_star_count() -> int:\n\treturn star_count\n\nfunc _update_label() -> void:\n\tstar_label.text = \"Stars: %d\" % star_count\n```\n\n### 2. `scripts/main_menu.gd` (UPDATED to v0.0.2 spec)\n```gdscript\nextends Node2D\n@onready var start_button: Button = $ColorRect/VBox/StartButton\nvar version_label := \"alpha-v0.0.2\"\n\nfunc _ready() -> void:\n\tstart_button.grab_focus()\n\nfunc _input(event: InputEvent) -> void:\n\tif event is InputEventKey and event.pressed and event.keycode == KEY_ENTER:\n\t\tget_tree().change_scene_to_file(\"res://scenes/main.tscn\")\n```\n\n### 3. `scenes/main_menu.tscn` (UPDATED to v0.0.2 spec)\nSimple menu with blue background, \"Camiel\" title, \"Start!\" button, and version label.\n\n### 4. `scripts/collectible.gd` (UPDATED)\nStar with bobbing animation, `collected` signal, hides on Camiel touch.\n\n### 5. `scenes/collectible.tscn` (UPDATED)\nArea2D with circle collision, star sprite, and AudioStreamPlayer for SFX.\n\n### 6. `scripts/finish_marker.gd` (UPDATED)\nArea2D flag that emits `finished` signal, plays finish SFX, shows \"Goed zo!\" message.\n\n### 7. `scenes/finish_marker.tscn` (UPDATED)\nVisual pole and flag with hitbox collision.\n\n### 8. `project.godot` (UPDATED)\n- Version: `alpha-v0.0.2`\n- Main scene: `res://scenes/main_menu.tscn`\n- Autoloads: `AudioManager` + `Accessibility`\n\n## Pre-existing Files (already at v0.0.3 level, remain compatible)\n- `scripts/audio_manager.gd` - Full implementation with BGM/SFX\n- `scripts/accessibility.gd` - High-contrast toggle\n- `assets/audio/README.md` - Audio asset documentation\n- `scenes/main.tscn` - Already has collectibles, finish marker, GameHUD\n- `scenes/collectible.tscn` / `scenes/finish_marker.tscn` - Already have proper collision shapes"
